1
00:00:00,133 --> 00:00:03,306
What Are Stars Like?
星星是什么样的

2
00:00:03,466 --> 00:00:07,693
Have you ever wondered about the stars?
你对星星感兴趣过吗

3
00:00:07,760 --> 00:00:11,706
In some ways, stars are like people.
在某些方面  星星就像人

4
00:00:11,786 --> 00:00:16,866
They are born. They grow old. And they die.
它们出生  它们变老  它们消亡

5
00:00:17,053 --> 00:00:21,413
A star is born from dust and gas.
星星是由尘埃和气体形成的

6
00:00:21,506 --> 00:00:25,760
Slowly the dust and gas make a ball.
慢慢地尘埃和气体形成了一个球

7
00:00:25,906 --> 00:00:28,733
The ball gets very hot.
球变得非常热

8
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:32,173
Then it starts to give off light.
然后它开始发光

9
00:00:32,293 --> 00:00:36,373
The young star grows into a giant.
年轻的星星变得巨大

10
00:00:36,506 --> 00:00:38,760
Many years go by.
许多年过去了

11
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:43,386
The older star begins to get small again.
较老的星星开始再次变小

12
00:00:43,533 --> 00:00:47,066
At last its light goes out.
最后它的光熄灭了

13
00:00:47,173 --> 00:00:51,173
The star's life is over.
这颗星星的生命结束了

